description: This is a Lego Video shown in a "Star Wars" like way that portrays Abraham and the almost sacrifice of Isaac (from the book of Genesis in the Bible).  This was used at GT Church's "Some Assembly Required" Vacation Bible School (VBS) in July 2009.  The four videos in this series were our first try at stop action filming.  Thank you to everyone who was involved.
